title: Maharishi Mahesh Yogi - Sage for a New Generation - by Alan Wait
description:
Maharishi Mahesh Yogi, Sage for a New Generation

Filmmaker Alan Waite was specifically commissioned by Maharishi Mahesh Yogi to make this film 
about TM in 1968. It won 'Best Documentary' in the 1969 Hollywood Film Festival, being noted for its 
'patchwork quilt' style.

His holiness Maharishi Mahesh Yogi first came to America in 1958, to start the TM Movement. Now, 
50 years later, there are TM centers in most of the free countries around the world.
